Package: postr
Title: Prepare reproducible posters using R Markdown
Version: 0.0.1.9000
Description: Templates and helper functions to prepare R Markdown based conference
    posters and produce output both in html for hosting and png for printing.
    Relies on the flexdashboard package to easily define poster layout.
